pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tracks\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its roughly 100 employees\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094among them: chemists, engineers and physicists\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094fashion some of the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s fastest, for Olympic Games and world championships.\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chemists\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"engineers\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"physicists\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094fashion\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Games\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"world championships\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are surfaces that can change slightly in shape, color and material but never shift in their shared overall focus to please the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s best with the factor they most care about: speed.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"surfaces\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"material\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"their shared overall focus\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the factor\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Track designs\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and actual tracks\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094take shape in this valley of grapes and castles, including Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s latest marquee creation.In Paris, the track and field portion of the Olympics will begin Aug. 1 (men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 20-kilometer race walk) and conclude Aug. 11 (women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s marathon).\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.927610083408223e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Track designs\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and actual tracks\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094take shape\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"this valley\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"grapes\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"castles\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"latest marquee creation\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the track and field portion\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"20-kilometer race walk\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In between, 46 of 48 total events will unfold on Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s latest track, which happens to be \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6purple.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"46 of 48 total events\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"latest track\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6purple\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Founded in 1948, Mondo formed from its earliest specialty: rubber flooring.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1019, \"end\": 1024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its earliest specialty\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It made its first Olympic track back in \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009976, for the Montreal Games.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its first Olympic track\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the Montreal Games\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo has built every subsequent Olympic track; this year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s marks iteration No.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every subsequent Olympic track\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"iteration No\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"13.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo helped move the sport from cinder tracks to synthetic versions.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1236, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"cinder tracks\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"synthetic versions\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It tested the latter for the first time in Montreal, after installing a version that had been developed for horse racing as a starting point.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1349, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.587178761147389e-14, \"text\": \"Montreal\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"a version\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"horse racing\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"a starting point\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Engineers have developed and tweaked Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s tech within that world ever since, which helped Mondo shift the sport again, into the more preferred vulcanized rubber surface enjoyed by today\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s stars.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Engineers\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"tech\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"that world\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"the more preferred vulcanized rubber surface\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"today\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s stars\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s place within this odd sports space expanded, so did its aims, the scale of its logistics and the level of coordination required to ensure quality control.\\u00c2 The structure of a prefabricated athletics track is complex.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"this odd sports space\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"its aims\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"the scale\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"its logistics\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"coordination\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"quality control\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"The structure\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"a prefabricated athletics track\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its upper layer ensures optimal contact between the shoe and the surface and water drainage; the lower layer, with a lower density to be compressible and air cells characterized by a precise geometric shape, works by accumulating and returning energy to the athlete.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its upper layer\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"optimal contact\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"the shoe\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"water drainage\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower layer\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"a lower density\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"compressible and air cells\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"a precise geometric shape\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The careful choice of material for the upper layer and the design of the shape of the lower air cells make it possible to identify the best compromise: accumulating enough energy to prevent injuries to athletes and reduce strain on their joints, but also accompanying the athletic gesture so that the energy is returned to the athlete in an ideal way for optimal execution.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The careful choice\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"material\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"the upper layer\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2202}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"the shape\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower air cells\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the best compromise\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"enough energy\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"strain\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"their joints\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletic gesture\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"an ideal way\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2502}, {\"ngram\": \"optimal execution\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most tracks are red-brick-clay in color (sometimes described as terracotta).\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most tracks\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"red-brick-clay\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"terracotta\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s changing, the shift never more dramatic than for the showcase taking place on an international, purple stage.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shift\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"the showcase taking place\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"an international, purple stage\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic organizers long ago noted the colors of these Games\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094purple, blue and green\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and asked if Mondo could incorporate them in some way.\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"the colors\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094purple\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"green\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"some way\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Short answer: Yes.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Short answer\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Studies were commissioned, in-depth analyses were embarked upon.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Studies\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"depth\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heavy attention went toward the color scheme, which needed to be decided early in the process so that patents could be submitted and any shade already under patent could be avoided or tweaked.\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 3147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Heavy attention\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"the color scheme\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"patents\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"any shade\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"patent\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even after choosing purple, varied tones needed to be considered.\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"purple, varied tones\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo settled on the lighter shade for the track itself, the darker shade for the service areas and the gray shade for turns at the end of bends, which reminded Parisian officials of pictures from the Paris Games in 1924.\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3214, \"end\": 3219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lighter shade\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"the service areas\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3309}, {\"ngram\": \"the gray shade\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"turns\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3349}, {\"ngram\": \"bends\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3358}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisian officials\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"pictures\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo tried out roughly 40 shades before selecting the versions it liked best.\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3437, \"end\": 3442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"roughly 40 shades\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"the versions\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Designers tested each not only for aesthetic quality, but also for how each reacted to external factors like UV rays, which wear out all colors at varying speeds over time.\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Designers\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"aesthetic quality\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"external factors\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3619}, {\"ngram\": \"UV rays\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"all colors\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"varying speeds\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3677}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo found no patent crossover in any of the shades that it selected.\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3689, \"end\": 3694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no patent crossover\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3720}, {\"ngram\": \"the shades\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It found that each was strong in UV resistance, especially when compared to other, also viable, purples.\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"UV resistance\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3806}, {\"ngram\": \"other, also viable, purples\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At that point, what Mondo executive Maurizio Stroppiana calls their \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbold move\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d could begin to take its oval shape.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3885, \"end\": 3890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}, {\"begin\": 3910, \"end\": 3920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999977981133, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stroppiana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3878}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbold\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"move\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3941, \"to\": 3948}, {\"ngram\": \"its oval shape\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The process, generally, works like this: Mondo execs coordinate with national federations and tournament hosts like World Athletics, a partner since 1987.\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 4140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4102, \"end\": 4117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0342369039047325e-27, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The process\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 3997}, {\"ngram\": \"Mondo execs coordinate\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4049}, {\"ngram\": \"national federations\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4075}, {\"ngram\": \"tournament hosts\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"a partner\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to host a world-class competition, Mondo must make about 150 other pieces\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094cages, carts, starting blocks, take-off boards, mattresses (to land on), hurdles (to jump over)\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094in addition to the surface.\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4185, \"end\": 4190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4149}, {\"ngram\": \"a world-class competition\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"about 150 other pieces\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094cages\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4231}, {\"ngram\": \"carts\", \"from\": 4233, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"blocks\", \"from\": 4249, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"take-off boards\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4272}, {\"ngram\": \"hurdles\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4306}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 4327, \"to\": 4335}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the purple track, that meant conversations with Olympic organizers, incorporating requests into designs, making decisions about the three colors (two shades of purple; one lighter, like lavender; the other, darker; another gray) and constructing 17,000 square meters of surface (nearly 183,000 square feet) along with a 7,200 square-meter warm-up track.\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the purple track\", \"from\": 4357, \"to\": 4373}, {\"ngram\": \"conversations\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4399}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4423}, {\"ngram\": \"requests\", \"from\": 4439, \"to\": 4447}, {\"ngram\": \"designs\", \"from\": 4453, \"to\": 4460}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4478}, {\"ngram\": \"the three colors\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4501}, {\"ngram\": \"two shades\", \"from\": 4503, \"to\": 4513}, {\"ngram\": \"purple\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4523}, {\"ngram\": \"lavender\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4551}, {\"ngram\": \"the other, darker\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4570}, {\"ngram\": \"another gray\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4584}, {\"ngram\": \"17,000 square meters\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4623}, {\"ngram\": \"surface\", \"from\": 4627, \"to\": 4634}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 183,000 square feet\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4662}, {\"ngram\": \"a 7,200 square-meter warm-up track\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Any one track is designed, in part, by several algorithms.\", \"from\": 4712, \"to\": 4770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Any one track\", \"from\": 4712, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4742, \"to\": 4746}, {\"ngram\": \"several algorithms\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When combined, they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re meant to aid decisions for optimal shape and ideal dimensions while incorporating seemingly miniscule details like the air cells inside the lower layers of the track and design tweaks that reduce energy loss, improving performance.\", \"from\": 4771, \"to\": 5027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 4786, \"to\": 4795}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 4809, \"to\": 4818}, {\"ngram\": \"optimal shape\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4836}, {\"ngram\": \"ideal dimensions\", \"from\": 4841, \"to\": 4857}, {\"ngram\": \"seemingly miniscule details\", \"from\": 4878, \"to\": 4905}, {\"ngram\": \"the air cells\", \"from\": 4911, \"to\": 4924}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower layers\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 4948}, {\"ngram\": \"the track and design tweaks\", \"from\": 4952, \"to\": 4979}, {\"ngram\": \"energy loss\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5003}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roughly eight years ago, Mondo began soliciting feedback from individual athletes and their teams.\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5053, \"end\": 5058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"feedback\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5084}, {\"ngram\": \"individual athletes\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5109}, {\"ngram\": \"their teams\", \"from\": 5114, \"to\": 5125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo also sought partners for specific improvements to its process.\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5128, \"end\": 5133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"partners\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5154}, {\"ngram\": \"specific improvements\", \"from\": 5159, \"to\": 5180}, {\"ngram\": \"its process\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One, a laboratory, works in granular detail on the first two layers of track asphalt, ensuring it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s properly designed, built and easy to lay down, perfectly flat.\", \"from\": 5197, \"to\": 5361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a laboratory\", \"from\": 5202, \"to\": 5214}, {\"ngram\": \"granular detail\", \"from\": 5225, \"to\": 5240}, {\"ngram\": \"the first two layers\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5264}, {\"ngram\": \"track asphalt\", \"from\": 5268, \"to\": 5281}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5292, \"to\": 5298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris track, for instance, marks the first time a track is primarily purple-hued.\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5366, \"end\": 5371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.927610083408223e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 5383, \"to\": 5391}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5413}, {\"ngram\": \"a track\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the glue used for tweaking the surface is purple.\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even the glue\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5461}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 5480, \"to\": 5491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stroppiana is the vice president of Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csports sector.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He recognizes his company\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s connections to the Olympic track stadium, Stade de France\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Mondo built its first track in 1998 and a newer version in 2003 for the world championships.\", \"from\": 5504, \"to\": 5753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5504, \"end\": 5514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999977981133, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stroppiana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\"}, {\"begin\": 5661, \"end\": 5666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vice president\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5536}, {\"ngram\": \"Mondo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5549}, {\"ngram\": \"his company\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s connections\", \"from\": 5585, \"to\": 5612}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic track stadium\", \"from\": 5616, \"to\": 5641}, {\"ngram\": \"its first track\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5688}, {\"ngram\": \"a newer version\", \"from\": 5701, \"to\": 5716}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows that roughly 74,000 people will filter daily inside a space so large it requiredtwomassive video screens, each about the size of regulation tennis courts, and needed 650 new light banks.\", \"from\": 5754, \"to\": 5949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"roughly 74,000 people\", \"from\": 5768, \"to\": 5789}, {\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 5815, \"to\": 5822}, {\"ngram\": \"so large it requiredtwomassive video screens\", \"from\": 5823, \"to\": 5867}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 5880, \"to\": 5888}, {\"ngram\": \"regulation tennis courts\", \"from\": 5892, \"to\": 5916}, {\"ngram\": \"650 new light banks\", \"from\": 5929, \"to\": 5948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo soon weighed its color and design choices alongside the minimum and maximum requirements laid out by the IOC.\", \"from\": 5951, \"to\": 6066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5951, \"end\": 5956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}, {\"begin\": 6062, \"end\": 6065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.954569350975857e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its color and design choices\", \"from\": 5970, \"to\": 5998}, {\"ngram\": \"the minimum and maximum requirements\", \"from\": 6009, \"to\": 6045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each related to myriad factors: compliance, energy absorption, durability and sustainability.\", \"from\": 6067, \"to\": 6160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"myriad factors\", \"from\": 6083, \"to\": 6097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next, Mondo began its surface-optimization.\", \"from\": 6162, \"to\": 6205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6168, \"end\": 6173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its surface-optimization\", \"from\": 6180, \"to\": 6204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then: building.\", \"from\": 6207, \"to\": 6222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then: measuring, analyzing, tweaking, adapting, finalizing.\", \"from\": 6224, \"to\": 6283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Then: measuring\", \"from\": 6224, \"to\": 6239}, {\"ngram\": \"finalizing\", \"from\": 6272, \"to\": 6282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then: installing more than 1,100 rolls of track that the factory shipped in April.\", \"from\": 6285, \"to\": 6367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than 1,100 rolls\", \"from\": 6302, \"to\": 6323}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 6327, \"to\": 6332}, {\"ngram\": \"the factory\", \"from\": 6338, \"to\": 6349}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 6361, \"to\": 6366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo officials don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t typically share detailed costs of any track; in part, because there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s nuance in the numbers.\", \"from\": 6369, \"to\": 6487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6369, \"end\": 6374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"score\": 0.9912827463525816, \"rank\": 0.008697681628842237, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_film\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 6385, \"to\": 6392}, {\"ngram\": \"detailed costs\", \"from\": 6409, \"to\": 6423}, {\"ngram\": \"any track\", \"from\": 6427, \"to\": 6436}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 6441, \"to\": 6445}, {\"ngram\": \"because there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s nuance\", \"from\": 6447, \"to\": 6471}, {\"ngram\": \"the numbers\", \"from\": 6475, \"to\": 6486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A safe range for costs associated with the purple track falls between two million and three million euro (roughly $2.2 million to $3.3 million).\", \"from\": 6488, \"to\": 6632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A safe range\", \"from\": 6488, \"to\": 6500}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 6505, \"to\": 6510}, {\"ngram\": \"the purple track\", \"from\": 6527, \"to\": 6543}, {\"ngram\": \"two million and three million euro\", \"from\": 6558, \"to\": 6592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stroppiana says this track landed in the same cost range as the last one in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6633, \"end\": 6643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999977981133, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stroppiana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\"}, {\"begin\": 6709, \"end\": 6714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999121355397, \"rank\": 8.784334361983627e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this track\", \"from\": 6649, \"to\": 6659}, {\"ngram\": \"the same cost range\", \"from\": 6670, \"to\": 6689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step, Stroppiana says, intends to highlight athletes, their performances and a sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s shift into faster-faster-faster times.\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6729, \"end\": 6739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999977981133, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stroppiana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every step\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6727}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6767, \"to\": 6775}, {\"ngram\": \"their performances\", \"from\": 6777, \"to\": 6795}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s shift\", \"from\": 6800, \"to\": 6817}, {\"ngram\": \"faster-faster-faster times\", \"from\": 6823, \"to\": 6849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bonus, Stroppiana says, is that this track, different and purple, is sure to elicit attention all on its own.\", \"from\": 6851, \"to\": 6964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6862, \"end\": 6872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999977981133, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stroppiana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bonus\", \"from\": 6851, \"to\": 6860}, {\"ngram\": \"this track\", \"from\": 6887, \"to\": 6897}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 6939, \"to\": 6948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAbsolutely beautiful,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says.\", \"from\": 6965, \"to\": 7001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cFantastic.\", \"from\": 7002, \"to\": 7015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cFantastic\", \"from\": 7002, \"to\": 7014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Iconic.\", \"from\": 7016, \"to\": 7023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Iconic\", \"from\": 7016, \"to\": 7022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it connects to the event.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The overall Mondo goal never changes: It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s to take the greatness inherent inNoah Lyles, Sydney McL