nformed Olympic officials of those one week before they shipped, causing some consternation.\", \"from\": 11718, \"to\": 11836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11718, \"end\": 11728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999977981133, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stroppiana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 11734, \"to\": 11742}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic officials\", \"from\": 11752, \"to\": 11769}, {\"ngram\": \"those one week\", \"from\": 11773, \"to\": 11787}, {\"ngram\": \"some consternation\", \"from\": 11817, \"to\": 11835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the patents went through\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Stroppiana says they would not have otherwise because presenting patents to a customer before the application is approved kills the application the minute the presentation starts.\", \"from\": 11837, \"to\": 12048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11869, \"end\": 11879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999977981133, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stroppiana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stroppiana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the patents\", \"from\": 11841, \"to\": 11852}, {\"ngram\": \"patents\", \"from\": 11934, \"to\": 11941}, {\"ngram\": \"a customer\", \"from\": 11945, \"to\": 11955}, {\"ngram\": \"the application\", \"from\": 11963, \"to\": 11978}, {\"ngram\": \"the application\", \"from\": 11997, \"to\": 12012}, {\"ngram\": \"the presentation\", \"from\": 12024, \"to\": 12040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, all one-thousand-or-so rolls were sent and installed on top of the fixed asphalt base with every other layer glued down (by some 2,800 pots of purple glue) in a matter of weeks.\", \"from\": 12050, \"to\": 12233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [